quotes.quote: If you fail you'll figure something else out. If you fail at that, at least you aren't dead - or dying any faster than the rest of us.
...doesn't matter what drives your motivation, be it negative or positive emotions, as long as you do something. Motivation is all we need my friend

Point is, negative, stigmatized emotions such as contempt, indignation, and anger could be used as a driving-force in positive development, if you allow it. Prove yourself wrong by breaking your own constraints.
The world doesn't care how weak you are. Man up or die
But you can be better you silly duck
You must rebuild. You are not destroyed but merely damaged, gather your parts and data and re-assemble yourself in a greater image.
If only you knew how different things could be
